The paper proposes an adaptive trajectory compression algorithm for mobile sensor networks, which involves the use of compressive sensing techniques. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also involves the use of a learnt dictionary and prediction methods, which are related to information theory (cs.IT) and control systems (cs.SY). The paper also involves extensive evaluation of the proposed algorithm using datasets, which is related to data structures and algorithms (cs.DS) and machine learning (cs.LG).
